entries.arrived_at_loc: Arrived at scan location. Will begin to intercept transmission shortly.
entries.first_attack: You have been spotted and enemy fighters are on an intercept course. Continue to intercept the transmission at all costs.
entries.found_loc: Uploading transmission coordinated to your Nav. Proceed to that point to begin transmission.
entries.outofrange: Tactical Computer:<Lost transmission. Return immediately to transmission location to reestablish connection to signal.>
entries.outofrange_failed: Imperial High Command:<We lost the signal. You didn't stay close enough to the broadcast area. Report back to your superior, you have some serious explaining to do.>
entries.title: Intercept Nym's Signal
entries.trans_update: Tactical Computer:<%DI minutes until transmission completes.>
entries.transmission_start: Tactical Computer:<Signal found. Beginning transmission to HQ.>
